    "read": "Kimi now has a real 20-step MBS1 retained gate. Top-8 standard-EP hot-helper helps over plain standard EP, but Primus-Turbo raw top-k no-helper is faster and lower-memory at MBS1. This does not invalidate the hot-helper mechanism at larger MBS, because the Kimi MBS2/4/8 ladder is not measured yet and DeepSeek MBS8 still favors hot-helper. Next Kimi work should extend the MBS ladder before claiming cross-model highest-MBS behavior."
